The evidence with the title 'Reparations for slavery debate in the United States - Wikipedia ' says Reparations for slavery is a proposal that some type of compensation should be provided to the descendants of enslaved people in the United States , in consideration of the forced and uncompensated labor their ancestors performed over centuries . This compensation has been proposed in a variety of forms, from individual  ... . Various estimates have been given if such payments were to be made . 
